      "@type": "asbval:ClaimAssessment",
      "asbval:evidence_quote": "PS2MS employs the DeepEI deep learning model to convert the analyte's mass spectrum into its corresponding fingerprint... A similarity metric based on the fingerprints of both the analyte and its derivatives can then be readily calculated.",
      "asbval:note": "Paper uses deep learning models (NEIMS, DeepEI) but does not explicitly extract or report softmax probabilities or prediction uncertainties. Instead, it computes SMSF (integrated similarity metric) as a ranking score. The paper reports similarity scores and ranking performance (RRP, relative ranking performance) rather than model confidence/uncertainty estimates.",
      "asbval:perspicacite_kb": "asb-paper-10-1021-acs-analchem-3c05019",
