      "@type": "asbval:ClaimAssessment",
      "asbval:evidence_quote": "The validation of PS2MS was carried out through anonymized testing of known synthetic cathinones, showcasing high specificity and sensitivity. Furthermore, the case study involving eutylone highlighted the challenges associated with closely related isomers.",
      "asbval:note": "Paper does perform stratification (positive vs. negative samples, cathinone vs. noncathinone) and reports sensitivity/specificity metrics, but does not explicitly stratify by structural novelty or out-of-distribution detection. The isomer challenge is noted but not addressed via confidence-score-based stratification.",
