      "asbval:note": "The paper does not discuss feature normalization or standardization as a preprocessing step. The paper focuses on enumeration of NPS derivatives, mass spectrum prediction using NEIMS and DeepEI, and similarity metric calculation. No mention of normalizing/standardizing input features before feeding them to deep learning models.",
