      "asbval:target_claim_field": "research_question",
      "asbval:target_claim_text": "Normalize or standardize encoded molecular features to match the numerical scale and distribution expected by a deep learning model's input layer. This ensures feature values fall within the model's training range, preventing saturation or numerical instability during inference.",
