      "asbval:note": "RDKit is not mentioned anywhere in the paper. The paper uses SMILES notation (passage 3) but does not name RDKit as the tool for parsing or feature extraction. The paper focuses on NEIMS and DeepEI for spectrum/fingerprint prediction, and SCScore for synthesis difficulty assessment. No evidence of RDKit usage in the paper.",
