      "asbval:note": "Paper performs SMILES-based structure manipulation and fingerprint generation from structural representations, but does not name the specific tool used. The functional role (structure parsing and descriptor extraction) is present in the paper's workflow, but the tool identity is not disclosed. Paper likely uses an unspecified cheminformatics library for this purpose, not necessarily RDKit.",
