    {
      "@id": "asbval:assertion/skill/statistical-distribution-analysis-across-cohorts/006",
      "@type": "asbval:ClaimAssessment",
      "asbval:evidence_quote": "Figure 3c. Distribution of different similarity metrics between the true and predicted data for the NIST test set... Figure 4b. Among the enumerated cathinones, the similarity score distributions for the cathinone-like drug \u03b1-PPP... Figure 5b. Distribution of the most similar similarity scores for one sample of Eutylone.",
      "asbval:note": "Paper does generate distribution visualizations (Figures 3c, 4b, 5b show distributions of similarity scores across cohorts). However, the paper does not specify whether Matplotlib or Seaborn was used, nor does it explicitly show box plots or violin plots\u2014the figures appear to be histograms or scatter plots of similarity score distributions.",
      "asbval:perspicacite_kb": "asb-paper-10-1021-acs-analchem-3c05019",
